{"tid":1787099,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【Can Bank】走私與嫖娼分別 - 散子","createTime":"2019-12-17T16:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T16:03:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6078bd04a120851ead78f9da1480ce6183b1b73b","tid":1787099,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191217/OKXJLDHV5AW5A37HQRGBHAXRAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191217%2FOKXJLDHV5AW5A37HQRGBHAXRAE%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BupSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=795a08be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191217%2FOKXJLDHV5AW5A37HQRGBHAXRAE%2F&h=37f8e30c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191217/OKXJLDHV5AW5A37HQRGBHAXRAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【Can Bank】走私與嫖娼分別 - 散子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191217/large/1576512463_d223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576512463_d223.jpg&h=eb9529e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再有港人在口岸過境時「被送中」，今次通道是港珠澳大橋。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n再有港人在口岸過境時「被送中」，今次通道是港珠澳大橋，事主上周五失蹤，到昨日珠海公安「承認責任」，指事主七年前涉嫌走私手機而被通緝，因而在上周五被捕。以目前緊張局勢，自然有人不太相信今次走私事件。<br />\n<br />\n今次港人涉及走私，最令人驚訝是案發時間是七年前，究竟中國刑事案有多長的追溯期？翻閱資料，內地刑法中追溯期最長為20年，視乎涉及案件可判刑期（香港刑事案無追溯期限；民事才有）。至於走私刑期則視乎應繳稅額，5萬至15萬元（人民幣，下同）三年；15萬至50萬元可判10年；50萬元以上可判無期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n至於上次英國駐港領使館僱員所涉「嫖娼」，並非犯罪行為，是行政違法行為，涉及治安管理處罰法，可以受到行政處罰，可以處以10至15日拘留，而他亦早已獲釋；但若明知自己有性病而嫖娼的，就涉及刑事，可處以五年以下有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n再參考銅鑼灣書店股東及員工的「洗頭艇」、醉駕導致他人死亡及潛逃的李波及桂民海，兩個不同罪名，一個早已獲釋，一個至今被囚禁。是否走私或嫖娼，只有當事人知道，但當局以甚麼理由作拘留或拘捕，則大概猜到當局打算把人留多久。<br />\n<br />\n散子<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BupSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=a62a6d2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/</a> 散子-257101397966975"},{"pid":"9e76ad45ddebed3c4b4f759c9d28a050bc50de8a","tid":1787099,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}